==Locked Transparency Options==
When locked transparency options are makred with an icon ( [[File:en/Manual/TransparencyOptions-a.png]] ), and are not affected by the <code>X</code> key. Locked options can still be toggled using clicking on the button, or using <code>ctrl</code>+(<code>1</code> to <code>9</code>). These may be unlocked using <code>ctrl</code>+<code>click</code> on the appropriate buttons.